# Exclude macOS AppleDouble metadata files — they live alongside files on
# NFS/SMB shared filesystems and Docker BuildKit's tar sender chokes on
# their xattrs ("failed to xattr ._data: operation not permitted") when the
# build context lives on macOS-shared NFS. The companion entry in
# `.gitignore` keeps them out of the repo.
**/._*
